NodeMongoAngular--coinservice
-----------------------------
#prerequisite-1
install node.js and check 
node -v -->example:v8.11.1
npm -v  --->example:5.6.0
#prerequisite-2
Mongo Database Installed(example:v3.4.6) and mongod.exe is executed
----------------------------------------
npm init -y
npm install --save mongodb@2.2.35
npm install restify@6.4.0 --save --no-optional
npm install restify-cors-middleware@1.1.0
node service.js